## 2026-05-05 вАФ Session N+47

**Tasks completed:** T197, T198

**Summary:**
All prior tasks (T001вАУT196) were complete. Created T197+T198 task specs then implemented two Phase 77 features: Season Performance Bonus (T197) and Trade Wind Events (T198).

**T197 вАФ Season Performance Bonus:**
- `src/systems/seasonPerformance.js`: New file. `initSeasonPerformance()` subscribes to SEASON_CHANGED *after* SeasonChronicle (registered first in boot), ensuring `completed[0]` is already populated. `_onSeasonChanged()` reads `battlesWon`, `battlesLost`, `built`, `techs`, `tilesGained`, `quests` from the just-completed recap. Awards morale: +2 per 3 wins (max 6), +2 per 2 builds (max 4), +4 if any tech completed, +3 per 5 tiles gained (max 6), +3 if quest completed, +2 peaceful bonus if battlesLost===0. Prestige = min(40, floor(scoreSum √Ч 0.25)) where scoreSum = wins√Ч5 + built√Ч3 + techs√Ч10 + tiles√Ч2 + quests√Ч5. Calls `changeMorale()` + `awardPrestige()`, adds an info message to the log, shows a 6-second windfall toast with emoji breakdown.
- `src/main.js`: Import + `initSeasonPerformance()` in boot() only (pure subscription, no per-game state to reset).

**T198 вАФ Trade Wind Events:**
- `src/systems/tradeWinds.js`: New file. 5 wind types: `silk_road` (+1.0 gold/s), `pirate_raids` (вИТ0.5 gold/s), `boom_season` (+0.8 gold/s +0.5 food/s), `supply_shortage` (вИТ0.4 iron/s), `merchant_boom` (+0.6 gold/s +0.3 iron/s). `initTradeWinds()` creates `state.tradeWind = {active, nextWindSeason, history, totalEvents}`; subscribes SEASON_CHANGED. `_onSeasonChanged()`: (1) expire active wind if `active.endsAtSeason === idx`; (2) only decrement `nextWindSeason` when no active wind (prevents immediate back-to-back respawn); (3) call `_spawnWind()` when counter reaches 0. `_spawnWind()` picks a non-repeating wind, sets `endsAtSeason = (idx+1)%4` (1-season lifetime), updates history (max 4 entries), emits windfall message + TRADE_WIND_CHANGED + recalcRates. `getTradeWindRateBonuses()` exported for resources.js.
- `src/core/state.js`: `tradeWind: null` declared in state object; `state.tradeWind = null` in `initState()`.
- `src/core/events.js`: `TRADE_WIND_CHANGED: 'tradeWindChanged'` added.
- `src/systems/resources.js`: `import getTradeWindRateBonuses` from tradeWinds.js; applied after Vizier rate bonuses in `recalcRates()` вАФ flat add to gold/iron/food rates.
- `src/ui/marketPanel.js`: Import `getActiveTradeWind + getTradeWindHistory`; added `on(Events.TRADE_WIND_CHANGED, _render)` listener; `_tradeWindSection()` appended to render вАФ shows active wind card (icon/name/desc/effect) or "Calm Seas" + last 4 historical winds.
- `src/main.js`: Import + `initTradeWinds()` in boot() + `_newGame()`; save version 65вЖТ66; `tradeWind` saved/loaded.
- `styles/main.css`: `.trade-wind-section`, `.trade-wind-header`, `.trade-wind-note`, `.trade-wind-calm`, `.trade-wind-card` (+`--active` variant), `.trade-wind-card__icon/body/name/desc/effect/until`, `.trade-wind-history` + entries.

**Architecture decisions:**
- T197 reads from SeasonChronicle's completed[0] rather than maintaining its own counters. The event subscription ordering (chronicle registered before performance in boot) guarantees completed[0] is fully populated. No per-game state needed.
- T198 uses season-index-based expiry (`endsAtSeason = (spawnSeason+1)%4`) rather than tick-based, which is simpler and naturally aligned to the season rhythm. The "only decrement when inactive" rule prevents a wind from expiring and spawning a replacement in the same SEASON_CHANGED call.
- Circular import (tradeWinds вЖФ resources) follows the established artisanGuilds/resources pattern вАФ safe because ES module circulars resolve at function-call time, not module-load time.

