- `src/data/buildings.js`: Added `relicShrine` unique building (minAge:3, requires manaWell√Ч1, cost 150g+100s+80m, production mana:0.3, unique=true). Placed before ancientMonument.
- `src/systems/relicShrine.js`: New file. `initRelicShrine()` lazy-creates `state.relicShrine = { nextPrestigeTick, communeCooldownUntil, totalCommunions, totalPrestigeAwarded }`. `relicShrineTick()` fires PRESTIGE_INTERVAL (240 ticks = 60s): awards `relicCount √Ч 12` prestige via `awardPrestige()`. `communeWithRelics()` validates building + cooldown, awards tier bonus (0=+20p, 1=+30p, 2-3=+50p+50g, 4-5=+80p+80g+5morale, 6=+150p+150g+10morale+5fog), sets cooldown, emits RELIC_SHRINE_COMMUNE + RESOURCE_CHANGED. `_revealFogTiles(n)` helper for the 6-relic tier. `getRelicCount()` + `getCommuneSecsLeft()` exported.
