- `game/src/ui/hud.js` вАФ Added `_prevValues` snapshot map and `FLASH_THRESHOLD = 40`. `renderHUD()` computes delta vs previous value per resource; calls `_flashEl()` with gain/loss class when `|delta| > 40`. `_flashEl()` force-reflows via `offsetWidth` to restart CSS animation and auto-removes class on `animationend`.
- `game/src/ui/buildingPanel.js` вАФ Added `data-building-id` attribute to all building card divs (locked and unlocked). `initBuildingPanel()` now wraps `BUILDING_CHANGED` handler to call `_popCard(id)` after re-render, applying `.building-card--popin` animation via reflow trick.
