**Architecture decisions:**
- Flash threshold (40) chosen to pass building costs (вЙ•50 resources) and loot grants (вЙ•50) while filtering per-tick income deltas (typically < 25 at max production).
- `void el.offsetWidth` (force reflow) is the standard CSS-only technique to restart a running animation without removing/re-adding the element.
- rAF loop in mapPanel is self-terminating (alpha вЙ§ 0 вЖТ clears `_flashRafId`) and guards against stacking loops with the `if (!_flashRafId)` check before starting.
