- `game/src/systems/resources.js` вАФ `_buildingProdMultiplier()`: extended to apply `divine_favor` √Ч1.3 to farm, `alchemy` √Ч1.25 to quarry, `economics` √Ч1.5 to market (stacks on `tradeRoutes` √Ч1.75), `alchemy` √Ч1.75 to manaWell (stacks on `arcane` √Ч2.0), `divine_favor` √Ч1.3 to manaWell (stacks with both). `recalcRates()`: added `if (state.techs.economics) caps.gold += 500` before territory bonus; trade route loop now reads `navMult = state.techs.navigation ? 1.5 : 1.0` and applies it to each route's income. `getBreakdown()`: trade route section updated to match with the same `navMult` logic so HUD tooltips show accurate figures.

