- `game/src/ui/mapPanel.js` вАФ Imported `UNITS`, `garrisonUnit`, `withdrawGarrison`, `getTotalGarrisoned`, `GARRISON_MAX_TOTAL`. `GARRISON_CHANGED` listener triggers re-render. `_drawTile` draws yellow рЯЫ°count in bottom-left corner. Tile tooltip shows garrison unit type + count + defense bonus. `_garrisonSection(x,y,tile)` builds picker HTML (existing garrison: unit badge + Withdraw; no garrison: per-unit-type buttons with food cost). All 3 picker states include garrison section. `_createImprovementPicker` handles `data-garrison` (station) and `data-withdraw-garrison` (withdraw) clicks.
- `game/src/main.js` вАФ `garrisons` added to `_save()` payload and `_applySave()` restore (`?? null`). Save version bumped 21 вЖТ 22.
- `game/styles/main.css` вАФ `.imp-garrison` gold-tinted container, `.imp-garrison__header/current/limit/units`, `.btn--garrison-unit` (gold hover), `.btn--garrison-withdraw` (red hover).

**Architecture decisions:**
- Ceasefire tick stored on each empire object (inside `state.diplomacy.empires[]`) вАФ automatically included in the existing `state.diplomacy` save payload without needing a separate top-level field.
- `payTribute` and `demandTribute` share the same `ceasefireTick` mechanism вАФ paying tribute buys peace, demanding tribute also triggers ceasefire (the faction is paying you, so they're not raiding). The distinction is directionality and gold gain/loss.
- Garrison units are removed from `state.units` (reducing attack power and army display) to make the positioning choice meaningful вАФ you trade mobile army strength for static defense.
- Garrison upkeep is calculated separately in `recalcRates()` (since garrisoned units are removed from `state.units`) to maintain economic balance.
- `GARRISON_MAX_TOTAL=10` prevents late-game abuse of garrisoning every tile; the 30 food/unit cost provides an upfront penalty discouraging casual overuse.
- `destroyGarrison()` is exported from `actions.js` (not `enemyAI.js`) to keep all state mutations in one module.

**Next session should tackle:**
- T069+: More Phase 7 features вАФ consider enemy faction tribute demands (AI demands tribute from player), unit merging/stacking improvements, or map territory analytics panel.

