- Mediation sets `sk.endsAt = state.tick` so `_skirmishTick()` resolves it on the same tick as the player action вАФ no separate "complete mediation" state needed.
- Gold reward for mediation is applied inside `_skirmishTick` (on the resolved event) to keep effect co-located with the resolution logic; prestige is awarded in main.js via the `BORDER_SKIRMISH` event listener (same pattern as other prestige awards).

