T191: Imperial Mint
----------------------------------------------------------------------
New unique Iron Age building (requires Economics tech + Market√Ч1; costs 150g+100s+80w;
+0.3 gold/s passive). Once per season, the player may convert surplus wood, stone, or
iron into gold at fixed rates (wood√Ч1.5, stone√Ч2, iron√Ч3), capped at 150 gold per
conversion. The cooldown resets automatically on every SEASON_CHANGED event. Market
panel shows an Imperial Mint section with per-resource conversion buttons showing
current stock, rate, and estimated gold yield. After conversion the section shows a
"Converted this season" badge until the next season.

