T192: Diplomatic Envoy
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Players can dispatch a single traveling envoy to any empire to improve relations over
8 minutes (1920 ticks). Cost: 80 gold. The envoy can be recalled at any time for a
40 gold refund. On arrival: warвЖТneutral (warScore reset), neutralвЖТallied (free alliance),
alliedвЖТ+15 favor. Only one envoy may be active. The Diplomacy panel shows a per-empire
envoy row: a progress bar with countdown when the envoy is en route to that empire, a
Recall button, and a Dispatch button (disabled when another envoy is already active).

