T193: Oracle of Fate вАФ Seasonal Omen System
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Every 6 minutes (Bronze Age+) the Oracle of Fate reveals one Prophetic Vision from
a pool of 5 omen types. Player has 60 seconds to Avert (pay gold), Channel (pay
mana for a positive boon), or Ignore (penalty fires). One omen active at a time.

Omen pool:
  вЪФпЄП  war_drums     вАФ raiders strike (lose 200вАУ350 gold). Avert 50g; Channel 30 mana (+20 morale).
  рЯМК  flood_tide    вАФ crops ruined (lose 150вАУ250 food + 80вАУ150 wood). Avert 40g; Channel 25 mana (+200 food).
  рЯМС  dark_eclipse  вАФ calamity (lose 300вАУ500 gold). Avert 60g; Channel 40 mana (+50 prestige +150 gold).
  рЯРН  viper_counsel вАФ treachery (вИТ20 morale + lose 60вАУ120 iron). Avert 50g; Channel 30 mana (+60 prestige +5 morale).
  вЭДпЄП  frost_blight  вАФ arcane loss (lose 100вАУ180 mana + 60вАУ120 stone). Avert 30g+20 mana; Channel 20 mana (+150 mana).

